# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:6
translate chinese emailwhitney_4ed503b7:

    # "I sit down in front of the laptop and open up the e-mail program."
    "我坐在笔记本电脑前，打开了邮件程序。"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:7
translate chinese emailwhitney_4885999e:

    # "The last email that Dad had received from her was the same day that I arrived back in town."
    "爸爸收到的她发来的最后那封邮件，正是我回到镇上的那天。"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:8
translate chinese emailwhitney_3f762033:

    # "\"Where are you? Please reply.\""
    "“你在哪儿？请回复。”"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:9
translate chinese emailwhitney_db5b4c3c:

    # "And that is it. No more correspondence."
    "仅此而已。再无往来。"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:10
translate chinese emailwhitney_957d73c5:

    # "I start writing."
    "我开始写邮件。"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:11
translate chinese emailwhitney_af04cae9:

    # "\"Whitney, my name is [pcname]. You have been talking to my dad for the last several months.\""
    "“惠特妮，我叫[pcname]。过去几个月你一直和我爸爸联系。”"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:12
translate chinese emailwhitney_0bc86332:

    # "\"He is now missing and I'm trying to find him.\""
    "“他现在失踪了，我正在找他。”"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:13
translate chinese emailwhitney_ce0bc1e0:

    # "\"I think that you know more about this than anybody else. Please contact me.\""
    "“我觉得你比任何人都更了解这件事。请联系我。”"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:14
translate chinese emailwhitney_2761510b:

    # "\"I have not given your information to the police yet, but I will soon.\""
    "“我还没把你的信息交给警方，但很快就会这么做。”"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:15
translate chinese emailwhitney_3dbffade:

    # "\"I just want to find my dad. Please help me.\""
    "“我只想找到我爸爸。请帮帮我。”"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:16
translate chinese emailwhitney_e24f0fa4:

    # "At the bottom of the e-mail I include my phone number, then I press send."
    "我在邮件末尾附上了我的电话号码，然后点击了发送。"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:18
translate chinese emailwhitney_722c8b04:

    # "I hope she responds. She is by far my biggest lead on what happened to my dad."
    "希望她能回复。她无疑是我目前关于父亲下落最重要的线索。"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:19
translate chinese emailwhitney_aa64e5fa:

    # "If she doesn't reply, I wonder if Jez or Adrian could help me track her down - trace IP addresses or something?"
    "如果她不回复，我不知道杰兹或阿德里安能不能帮我找到她——比如追踪IP地址之类的？"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:20
translate chinese emailwhitney_9c657a5a:

    # "For now, I'll give her a few days to get back to me."
    "眼下，我先给她几天时间回复我。"

